flowchart TD
    U[User / NOC Engineer] --> API[FastAPI Service]
    API --> AUTH[Auth / Request Validation]
    AUTH --> LG[LangGraph Agent Workflow]

    LG --> IG[Input Guard]
    IG --> IC[Intent Classifier]
    IC --> EE[Entity Extractor]
    EE --> PL[Planner]
    PL --> TR[Tool Router]

    TR --> RAG[RAG Retrieval Tool]
    TR --> SQL[PostgreSQL KPI Tool]
    TR --> KG[Neo4j Graph Tool]
    TR --> CASE[Historical Case Tool]
    TR --> OSS[Mock OSS API Tool]

    RAG --> EMB[Embedding Model]
    EMB --> VDB[(FAISS / Milvus)]
    SQL --> PG[(PostgreSQL KPI DB)]
    KG --> NEO[(Neo4j Telecom Graph)]
    CASE --> CASEDB[(Vector Case Library)]
    OSS --> OSSDB[(Mock OSS Data)]

    RAG --> EF[Evidence Fusion]
    SQL --> EF
    KG --> EF
    CASE --> EF
    OSS --> EF

    EF --> DR[Diagnosis Reasoner]
    DR --> REF{Reflection: Enough Evidence?}

    REF -- No: Need More Evidence --> TR
    REF -- Yes --> RG[Report Generator]
    RG --> OUT[Structured Diagnosis Report]
    OUT --> API
    API --> U

    LG --> TRACE[(Trace Store)]
    API --> FB[Feedback API]
    FB --> EVAL[(Evaluation Dataset)]
    EVAL --> METRIC[Metrics Dashboard]

    subgraph Data Sources
      PG
      NEO
      VDB
      CASEDB
      OSSDB
    end

    subgraph Agent Core
      IG
      IC
      EE
      PL
      TR
      EF
      DR
      REF
      RG
    end
